{"tid":241623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（重開）［陰謀論］有一班人想拖低網民質素","createTime":"2017-05-13T09:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T12:24:07.000Z","uid":9053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1adffb4d5d10dab54a4fd38b3e30f333f43ab0d0","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"今次開番岩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排發生嘅種種案件，包括車禍、強姦<br />\n<br />\n總有一班人搶住出黎批判，扮理性，然後有班羊群會跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，呢幾年高登言論成為大趨勢，好多網媒，例如一百毛果啲，密密mon住呢到，總之呢度講咩，都會俾人注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，報紙經常以網民、90後、後生仔涵蓋晒一小部分出位言論<br />\n<br />\n換言之，只要有搶眼言論，例如反社會、偏激意見，就會被炒作、被標籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而呢啲係可以製造出黎</span>"},{"pid":"f2dfb0fd786f12af8516cd00a5ac32089bb87c38","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，未打完出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而呢啲言論就會成為呢班人嘅標籤<br />\n<br />\n最終目的係咩？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扮自己人，扣你地帽子，製造你地萎靡不堪嘅形象</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"652a52dbb2d0df072763cc6eee67532c9eadcaf1","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身廢老眼中，你地做咩都係「細路仔」、「冇經驗」、「食鹽多過你食米」<br />\n<br />\n依家形象差到咁，無論政治方面，定係純粹自身層面<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅野都更加被定形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地就係牛鬼蛇神</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/170441_24a34a09cfe65c6d6eb5b9d6cff6f6b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F170441_24a34a09cfe65c6d6eb5b9d6cff6f6b6.jpg&h=661780b5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"38074aead9fa3ed407fd3d8981aa5b1673d63811","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔想我地咩都冇做過，就變成牛鬼蛇神<br />\n<br />\n無論係小學雞又好，做緊野又好<br />\n<br />\n請你地唔好以為網上講嘅野就係真心<br />\n<br />\n以為連登講嘅野就係真理</blockquote>"},{"pid":"60666700f6f16ab7f2aa937e23262ba64c13f60d","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛、共狗死全家</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d1012d76d5aed4b1612348bf12198a0d56b28917","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:47:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56eefe09d44efaa793c1a384b9639960beab51de","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc4c46fe0b3031dc277852a443a27d2b58f51a87","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c86f7b889c82013f5d50dc06faa14b8e8152d15d","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe344888c60e498c1562c4d959423bc93e9aab0a","tid":241623,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:48:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8042e613e95876c074fb344e0c5bb1d27e242a0","tid":241623,"u